BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (The postpartum period \(often called the 'fourth trimester'\) is a time of enormous) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (physical, emotional, and social change. Your body has done something extraordinary, and it) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (deserves intentional care as it heals. This guide supports you through recovery with) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (practical tools and compassionate guidance.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 624.2 Td (Remember: Recovery is not linear, and you do not need to 'bounce back.' You are becoming) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 610.2 Td (someone new - a mother. Give yourself grace.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
