BT /F2 12 Tf 54 674.2 Td (Timeline of Physical Recovery) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 652.2 Td (Week 1-2: Immediate Healing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 636.2 Td (- Uterus begins contracting back to size) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 622.2 Td (- Lochia \(postpartum bleeding\) is heaviest) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 608.2 Td (- Perineum or incision healing begins) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 594.2 Td (- Breast milk comes in \(days 2-5\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580.2 Td (- Hormone crash \(baby blues possible\)) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 562.2 Td (Weeks 2-6: Early Recovery) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 546.2 Td (- Bleeding gradually decreases) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 532.2 Td (- Energy slowly returns) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 518.2 Td (- Breastfeeding establishing \(or bottle feeding routine\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 504.2 Td (- Sleep deprivation peaks) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 490.2 Td (- 6-week postpartum check-up) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 472.2 Td (Months 2-6: Continued Healing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 456.2 Td (- Core and pelvic floor strengthening) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 442.2 Td (- Hormones gradually stabilizing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 428.2 Td (- Hair changes \(postpartum shedding around month 3-4\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 414.2 Td (- Gradual return to exercise) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 396.2 Td (Months 6-12+: Full Recovery) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 380.2 Td (- Full healing takes 12-18 months \(not 6 weeks\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 366.2 Td (- Body composition changes may be permanent - and that's okay) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 352.2 Td (- Mental health needs ongoing attention) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 322.4 Td (Red Flags - Seek Immediate Medical Care) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 304.4 Td (- Heavy bleeding \(soaking a pad in 1 hour or large clots\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 290.4 Td (- Fever over 100.4F) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 276.4 Td (- Severe headache or vision changes) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 262.4 Td (- Thoughts of harming yourself or baby \(call 988 or go to ER\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 248.4 Td (- Signs of infection \(foul smell, increasing pain, redness\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 234.4 Td (- Chest pain or difficulty breathing) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 220.4 Td (- Calf pain or swelling \(possible blood clot\)) Tj ET
endstream
