BT /F1 10 Tf 54 438.6 Td (- Egg muffins \(batch cook for the week\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 424.6 Td (- Rotisserie chicken with pre-washed salad) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 410.6 Td (- Trail mix with nuts, seeds, dried fruit) Tj ET
