96 0 obj
<< /Length 2779 >>
stream
BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Frequently Asked Questions) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 676.2 Td (Q: When will I feel like myself again?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 660.2 Td (The 'new normal' develops gradually over 6-12 months. You may not return to your pre-baby) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 646.2 Td (self - you're becoming a new version. Be patient and compassionate with this) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 632.2 Td (transformation.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 604.4 Td (Q: Is it normal to not feel bonded to my baby immediately?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 588.4 Td (Yes. Bonding is not always instant. It develops over time through care, skin-to-skin) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 574.4 Td (contact, and attentive presence. If bonding difficulties persist, talk to your provider.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 546.6 Td (Q: When can I exercise again?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 530.6 Td (Light walking can start days after vaginal birth \(when comfortable\). More structured) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 516.6 Td (exercise after 6-week clearance. C-section requires longer recovery. Always start gentle.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 488.8 Td (Q: How do I know if I have postpartum depression vs. baby blues?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 472.8 Td (Baby blues resolve within 2 weeks. PPD persists, worsens, or begins after 2 weeks. If) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 458.8 Td (symptoms interfere with functioning or bonding, or include thoughts of harm - seek help) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 444.8 Td (immediately.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 417.0 Td (Q: Is breastfeeding supposed to hurt?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 401.0 Td (Initial tenderness is common, but persistent pain is NOT normal and usually indicates) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 387.0 Td (latch issues. See a lactation consultant. Fed is best - however you choose to feed your) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 373.0 Td (baby.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 345.2 Td (Q: When will my body look normal again?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 329.2 Td (Your body grew a human. It may never look exactly the same, and that's okay. Focus on how) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 315.2 Td (you FEEL rather than how you look. Give yourself at least 12-18 months before evaluating.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 287.4 Td (Q: How do I accept help?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 271.4 Td (Practice saying 'yes' to every offer. Be specific: 'Could you bring a meal?' or 'Could you) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 257.4 Td (hold baby while I shower?' People want to help - let them. This is not weakness.) Tj ET
BT /F2 11 Tf 54 229.6 Td (Q: Is it normal to feel overwhelmed?) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 213.6 Td (Absolutely. New parenthood is one of life's biggest transitions. Overwhelm is expected.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 199.6 Td (It's not normal to feel hopeless, to not eat/sleep at all, or to have thoughts of harm -) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 185.6 Td (those need professional support.) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
